{"tid":1531011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日貼班仆街既地址出黎，究竟有冇人真係做？","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:44:08.000Z","uid":71253,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1f36d9c6d19f2005ebc75fba15775b011b9b8b","tid":1531011,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"明面做野短時間內未必做到<br />\n但呢D去搞鳩仆街既野有幾個人係街見佢都做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d6EWEZPO28Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd6EWEZPO28Q&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR20BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=e8c9775b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d6EWEZPO28Q</a><br />\n定佢地根本唔出街？<br />\n<br />\n甚至係屋外貼下野用膠水整壞佢個鎖都已經有排玩<br />\n講明先，唔住個橦樓既唔好做，做都唔好搭lift<br />\n<br />\n係目前未對政府做到咩傷害之前，應該要對呢D仆街落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1128fe1b5bbfc4d7ff4913eb6c6ce6e43271a1","tid":1531011,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"住同一棟大廈既, 最基本唔該係佢上下幾層既lift口貼滿街招"},{"pid":"9ce3baf8881fc6070862b1dc73a5e734298d1d2e","tid":1531011,"uid":241567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"門口實有cam 小心"},{"pid":"6ba20792a557b89499cce956dc213d0a0af80fc5","tid":1531011,"uid":71253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc1128fe1b5bbfc4d7ff4913eb6c6ce6e43271a1","tid":1531011,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"住同一棟大廈既, 最基本唔該係佢上下幾層既lift口貼滿街招"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"痴佢做左咩仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吱膠水入去個鎖匙lon到"},{"pid":"8a5e5409083adc49cf80f01315cef1a88439c8a1","tid":1531011,"uid":71253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ce3baf8881fc6070862b1dc73a5e734298d1d2e","tid":1531011,"uid":241567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"門口實有cam 小心"},